Description: The challenge provides a Python script (ende.py), an encrypted file (pole.txt), and a password file. The goal is to use the script to decrypt the file and obtain the flag.

Solution:

Download all provided files using wget.

Check the script usage:

python3 ende.py -h

The help message shows that files can be decrypted using:

python3 ende.py -d [file]

Decrypt the encrypted file:

python3 ende.py -d pole.txt

When prompted for a password, view the contents of password.txt:

cat password.txt
Enter the password into the script.
The script decrypts the file and prints the flag.

Key Concept: Understanding command-line arguments and using a Python script to decrypt a file with a provided password.
